  "code": "%%{Education_ClassroomService}}}%%\n\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [Education_LMS_Portal] --> Idle\n    \n    Idle --> Monitoring: CRON tick / YieldSnapshot event\n    \n    Monitoring --> Comparing: Collect APY data\n    \n    Comparing --> NoAction: APY diff < 0.5%\n    Comparing --> SmallRebalance: APY diff >= 0.5% && change < 50%\n    Comparing --> LargeRebalance: APY diff >= 0.5% && change >= 50%\n    \n    NoAction --> Idle: emit RebalanceSkipped\n    \n    SmallRebalance --> Executing: emit Callback(Education_StudentDB)\n    \n    LargeRebalance --> PendingFinality: Queue rebalance\n    PendingFinality --> PendingFinality: Wait 64 blocks\n    PendingFinality --> Executing: Finality reached\n    \n    Executing --> Completed: Rebalance executed\n    Completed --> Idle: Reset\n    \n    note right of Monitoring\n        Every ~12 minutes\n        or on manual trigger\n    end note\n    \n    note right of PendingFinality\n        Safety measure for\n        large TVL changes\n    end note\n",
